The market is also influenced by the evolving preferences in deployment modes, with a noticeable shift towards cloud-based solutions due to their scalability, flexibility, and cost-efficiency benefits. This shift reflects the growing need for interoperability and streamlined operations within ambulatory care settings. On-premise solutions still hold relevance for organizations prioritizing data control and customization.

